schools.name: Pioneer Magnet School for the Visual and Performing Arts

data.description: BEAUTIFUL LOCATION. Move in ready custom home in scenic Pioneer. Open room concept enhances the natural light throughout, spacious kitchen, formal dinning, 3-4 bedrooms or an office & 2 bathrooms providing ample room for all your family or guests needs.  Grand ensuite with huge walk-in closet, luxurious jetted tub, stall shower, double sinks that opens out to deck. Cozy up to the built-in fireplace with rock hearth, perfect for those chilly evenings.  From the back deck, you'll relish in the peace and tranquility of your surroundings, creating an ideal spot for relaxation and entertaining. This home is equipped with a whole-house GENERAC GENERATOR and SOLAR, ensuring you have power when you need it. Plus, it's part of a FIREWISE community, enhancing safety and peace of mind.      Don't miss the incredible opportunity to make this property your forever home. Its proximity to Kirkwood Resort, Lake Tahoe, the Wine Region, Silver Lake, and all the other attractions the Sierra's have to offer makes it an ideal location for those seeking a balanced and fulfilling lifestyle. Please independently verify the accuracy of all information provided.
